{
  "stem": "1141.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, they started screaming and running out, and they were shot to death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this is why we tried to-- to keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's how we survived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were mothers and sisters and brothers-- mothers and-- mothers and daughters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I witnessed some horrible situations, where the daughters were stealing the-- the bread from their mothers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- we-- we got that bread, and we would just take a bite and put it away for later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when we were starving, so we can have something in our stomachs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the mothers were already sleeping, their daughters took the bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would-- I prefer not to talk about this situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we-- the three of us, we stuck together to keep warm, to keep sane, and that's how we managed to get through that period.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can honestly tell you they felt terribly guilty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tried to-- they were afraid to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They realized that the war is approaching-- the-- the war is coming to an end, and they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of them, particularly, was extremely vicious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a very tall, extremely awkward, ugly-looking man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to go out and beating people for no reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a wooden stake hanging down from the side of his pants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he hit you-- you-- we had no-- we only were bones with skin, and it really used to break bones with that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- they couldn't lift those shovels with-- with the earth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and when he realized that we were falling apart, he would just yell out, [NON-ENGLISH]-- you know, go out, go on.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
